uchindrane nonfictionedit  translations  imitations of german ballads librivox audio – the border antiquities of england and scotland – a work coauthored by luke clennell and john greig with scotts contribution consisting of the substantial introductory essay originally published in  volumes from  to  – essays on chivalry romance and drama – a supplement to the – editions of the encyclopædia britannica  pauls letters to his kinsfolk – provincial antiquities of scotland – lives of the novelists – the journal of sir walter scott  the letters of malachi malagrowther  the life of napoleon buonaparte  religious discourses  tales of a grandfather being stories taken from scottish history – the st installment from the series tales of a grandfather  the history of scotland volume i  tales of a grandfather being stories taken from scottish history – the nd installment from the series tales of a grandfather  essays on ballad poetry  the history of scotland volume ii  tales of a grandfather being stories taken from scottish history – the rd installment from the series tales of a grandfather  letters on demonology and witchcraft  tales of a grandfather being stories taken from the history of france – the th installment from the series tales of a grandfather see alsoedit wikiquote has quotations related to walter scott wikisource has original works written by or about walter scott poetry portal operas inspired by walter scott jedediah cleishbotham fictional editor of tales of my landlord and scotts alter ego g a henty alessandro manzoni alexandre dumas père karl may baroness orczy rafael sabatini emilio salgari samuel shellabarger lawrence schoonover jules verne frank yerby gwr waverley class steam locomotives famous scots series principal clerk of session and justiciary writers museum referencesedit  family background retrieved    a b c d e edinburgh university library  october  homes of sir walter scott x edinburgh university library retrieved  july    cone t e  was sir walter